Tangerine (1979)

Categories: Classic
Date Added: 1979
(758 Mb)

The story of high society hostess named Tangerine and her three 'teenage daughters' Faith, Hope and Charity. Tangerine throws lavish parties at her sumptuous seaside home for influential business executives. What she is really up to, however, has more to do with dollars than hospitality . Her bait, Faith, Hope and Charity, who pretend to be between the ages of 13 and 15, are actually not teenagers at all, and are no relation to Tangerine whatsoever. It's a good, spicy tale and a provocative experience, as you follow the three 'nymphettes' In Their Erotic seduction
